{"tid":146261,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"節日同生日無我份 得番腦魔仔陪我","createTime":"2017-03-07T02:53:51.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-08T01:54:02.000Z","uid":72212,"like":3,"dislike":34,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"ad72d0c05d93843624dbb764431ace5b1a7c5b9d","tid":146261,"uid":72212,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T02:53:51.000Z","msg":"我就生日啦 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n可惜年年都無人陪我過<br />\n上年仲要醫院過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n習慣左生日快樂 禮物 一餐飯都無架啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n情人節真係好妒忌人地一對對<br />\n幾醜樣幾肥既女仔身邊都有人陪<br />\n話咁快又314 又生日<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n連住上<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過算啦 毒撚有乜資格妒忌人<br />\n永遠都一個人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/z.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n不過最近多左個新朋友<br />\n佢就係腦魔啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n買左佢番黎 望住佢果個又淫又開心既樣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n負面情緒都小左啲.<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/03/07/105205_ceea9f75e3f7d3f48e685df56e6aa5e0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F03%2F07%2F105205_ceea9f75e3f7d3f48e685df56e6aa5e0.jpg&h=c2188c8d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n係未好可愛好得意呢?<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n有啲想草哂佢成套<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f68bbc24f69aaf92557b7080f2bca7c85e10e26e","tid":146261,"uid":23160,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T02:54:56.000Z","msg":"直線賣腳"},{"pid":"fc152330d334ff078a13001be52c79b1bf037ff0","tid":146261,"uid":51594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-07T02:54:56.000Z","msg":"絲打收唔收兵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=